HTML :                  controls the structure of a webpage
CSS  :                  controls the presentation of a webpage
Javascript:             controls the behavior of a webpage
HTML tags:              add elements to webpage
HTML tag examples:      <button>, <img>, <p>,
container tags:         surrounds content for the elements
empty tags:             elements that are defined with only one tag
empty tags examples:    <img>
nested element:         putting element inside another element
radio element:         button that allows user to select one option
checkbox element:      allows user to select multiple options
